                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301209-259-defend2166 t18301209-259-deflabel1459"></join> in his family, but had left it - on the 9th of December she called, and said she had seen my master in the morning, and he had appointed to meet her at three o'clock; I said my master was not then at home, and she had better go into the office, as we are not allowed to let any one remain in the kitchen - one of the clerks then knocked at the door; I went and let him in, and when I returned to the kitchen the prisoner was just going out; I missed a tea-spoon - I took the prisoner's arm, said she must have it, and desired her to give it up without more words - she gave it from her bosom or her pocket; this is it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. His wife had got the situation that I held, and he thought I wanted to get back again - that is the reason he says this.</p>
